Angular - Front end framework
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Angular is a powerful front-end framework developed by Google for building dynamic, modern web applications.

Installation and New Project
----------------------------
cmd -> npm install -g @angular/cli (global system installation)
cmd -> ng --version (check the current version of angular)
sys -> locate the project path
cmd -> ng new <project-name>
cmd -> cd <project-name>
cmd -> ng serve --open (run application)

Commands (note: inside project folder) 
---------
cmd -> ng generate component <component-name>